Package: veja-bass-cab-lv2
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: VeJa Bass Cabinets LV2 plugin (pistomp fork)
 Bass guitar cabinet impulse response convolver with multiple speaker
 models embedded as compiled data. Patched to support arbitrary JACK
 period sizes (64, 128, 256+) via a generalized overlap-add implementation.
